{
  "texts": [
    "• Require answers to refer to specific references to published journal articles.",
    "o Students could iteratively direct ChatGPT to include information from specific references by copying reference abstracts or paragraphs as required.",
    "While generative text methods seem likely to become an integral tool in many facets of the future, it is important to evaluate capabilities of LLMs across many topics and response types before relying on these new tools for accurate information.",
    "This is especially true for use of LLM's in education or as a reference resource, as entirely false responses can be near-indistinguishable from fact.",
    "The high accuracy that we observe in GPT-4 responses to graduate-level examination questions demonstrate the model's capability to generate correct answers to many expert-level scientific questions."
  ]
}